'''Ferhat Mehenni''', d aselway n [[Amussu i Timanit n Tmurt n Iqbayliyen|Umussu i Timanit n Tmurt n Iqbayliyen]] (MAK), ilul-d deg [[5 Meɣres]] [[1951]] deg taddart n Illula, deg tama n temdinin n [[Buzegan]], [[Iɛezzugen]], akk-d [[Aqbu]]. 

Asmi i d-kemmel almad-ines deg Tesdawit n [[Lezzayer]] (tamaneɣt) yebda-d tikli-ines di ccna deg 1973 imi yewwi tarrazt tamezwarut n tafaska tatrart n ccna n Lezzayer. 
Kra n lweqt mbeɛd isbeggen-d iman-is belli yella mgal anabad n iɣil n Lezzayer imi yebda-d abrid n tigwin; ɣef igiten agi yekcem-d ɣef lḥebs 13 iberdan.

Mbeɛd [[Tafsut Taverkant]], imi Tamselta n Lezzayer tenɣa yiwen weqcic amelsi yettusemman [[Masinisa Germaḥ]], Ferḥat Mhenni isbed ''Amussu i Timanit n Tmurt''; tuddsa ixeddmen akken a tessiwed ar timanit n tmurt n el Kvayel. Llan wid i qqaren belli ɣef demma n wannecta i yettwanɣa mmi-s Ameẓian Mhenni deg 2004.

Amussu i Timanit n Tmurt (MAK), [[Agraw i Yedles d Tugdut]] (RCD), akk-d [[Tirni Iɣallen Inemlayen]] (FFS) d ikabaren isertiyen i sɛan ccan deg [[Tamurt n leqbayel|Tmurt n Izwawen]].

